{"tid":676604,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"神愛世人😇","createTime":"2018-05-24T13:36:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T16:06:37.000Z","uid":174115,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1a57462e90ca0d9ae2ea792b54caec8e1b44c1","tid":676604,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"甚至將祂的獨生子賜給他們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n叫一切信祂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n不致滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n反得永生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信個個都有病</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前細個冇得揀 日撚日比班教畜洗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話唔信耶穌就落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我心諗，如果佢真係愛你，<br />\n就唔會眼白白睇住你去一個充滿毒蛇猛獸既火山口，不理哭叫，不理哀號號<br />\n狠狠地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、毫無憐憫地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，用腳一伸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塞入去火紅既岩漿𥚃頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁又點叫做「神愛世人」呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a97a2419d92cde9e9e6b2fe9f93204d7940512b","tid":676604,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:36:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7PfXEk2rOwo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7PfXEk2rOwo&d=ODzoBClKuUbIDIRA1jo5X10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=dcaa2187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7PfXEk2rOwo</a>"},{"pid":"8f34d5cbead5cbe2717fa281243ca28d29d65e9b","tid":676604,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"神既試煉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020ac86c92f59e6f52aa2aa6f7de9fec0dfbc7e3","tid":676604,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一冇J圖就冇人回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d49ff33b12d9b00a15d451024dd75dd33c3dcf2","tid":676604,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"020ac86c92f59e6f52aa2aa6f7de9fec0dfbc7e3","tid":676604,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一冇J圖就冇人回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa3955b01dd381664c2b273b6b7049ab356a37e","tid":676604,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T14:05:46.000Z","msg":"上帝是真實的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/670047/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/670047/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb731dbc58b7f07f21905b8c368835ba444aec0","tid":676604,"uid":174115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7aa3955b01dd381664c2b273b6b7049ab356a37e","tid":676604,"uid":137555,"like":0,"dislik